    "detail": "I have stayed at ARTotel at least 15 times in the last 6 months, it’s my first choice for a reasonably priced hotel in Sanur when I am diving there. The rooms are all quite modern and well equipped, the roof top pool is nice but can get busy in peak times. The hotel is only a short stroll away from the beach and there are some great restaurants nearby within a few hundred yards - it’s on the quieter end of Sanur if you want lots of restaurants or bars but it’s a few dollars in a cab and they aren’t hard to get if that’s the case. The staff are the friendliest I’ve encountered in any hotel in Bali ",
